title: The Lone Ranger S01E09-E10
description:
The Lone Ranger

The Sole Survivor of a posse of Texas Rangers ambushed by a gang of desperados, John Reid was left for dead and nursed back to health by Tonto (Jay Silverheels), a friendly Indian whom he had once helped. With a black mask and silver bullets from the mine he discovered with his brother, one of the slain Rangers, Reid sets out astride his horse, Silver, to right the wrongs of the West as The Lone Ranger (Clayton Moore)

Episode 09 Tenderfeet

In "The Tenderfeet", Dick (Rand Brooks) and Bob Larrabee (Ross Ford) come West seeking silver and find villainy, as Hardrock Jones (Ray Bennet) frames them for killing his partner, Rusty Bates (Hank Worden). Then,

Episode 10 High Heels

Directed by Western Veteran George Archainbaud, "High Heels" finds the Ranger probing an attempt to stir up trouble between two good friends, John St. Ives (Jerome Sheldon ) and Dave Engles (Stanley Andrews). 

Approximately 46 Minutes 
Converted from VHS
